    "description": "We at Panchshil Realty Asia Pacific Associates are looking for an experienced Business Development Manager based out of Kochi. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Panchshil Realty Asia Pacific Associates:\nPanchshil Realty Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Prepare presentations and proposals for institutional clients\n• Provide advisory services on property investment and market trends\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n• Manage RERA documentation and compliance requirements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n• Proficiency in Investment Analysis\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in Portfolio Management\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Property Management\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Learning & development budget\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kochi, Kerala, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Panchshil Realty Asia Pacific Associates!",
